QuestData.Title: Coldheart Flight Routes
QuestData.Description:
<These diagrams contain detailed information concerning the patrols of the Mawsworn Kyrian.
Ve'nari would relish this knowledge.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring the Coldheart Flight Routes to Ve'nari at Ve'nari's Refuge.
QuestData.RewardText:
This will help mitigate the Mawsworn's aerial advantage. Caution must still be exercised, of course.
Do try to avoid their notice whenever possible. I would hate for one of them to follow you here.
